60
00:05:27,833 --> 00:05:33,500
such as those that permit comparisons of the registers of perceptions

61
00:05:33,008 --> 00:05:37,041
with the registers of representations

62
00:05:38,009 --> 00:05:45,015
and with those that necessarily accompany "retentions" or memories of the same.

63
00:05:47,004 --> 00:05:51,437
